<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>لَوْ تَصْعَدِينَ إِلَى الْقَمَرْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>لَوْ تَصْعَدِينَ إِلَى الْقَمَرْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَرِحَ الْقَمَرْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لَكِنَّ شَمْسَ الْكَوْنِ تَحْزَنُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>إِذْ ضِيَاؤُكِ سَوْفَ يُغْنِي الَبَدْرَ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>عَنْ ضَوْءِ الشُّمُوسِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>يَظَلُّ يَنْهَلُ مِنْ ضِيَائِكِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>ثُمَّ يَبْعَثُهُ يُنِيرُ الْكَوْنَ يَلْتَهِمُ الدُّجَى<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَيَحَارُ شِعْرِي مَا يَقُولْ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#006d98">أَيَقُولُ:</span> أَنْتِ الْبَدْرُ فِي أَيَّامِ بِيضٍ رَائِعَهْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#006d98">أَيَقُولُ:</span> أَنْتِ الشَّمْسُ قَدْ ظَهَرَتْ بِلَيْلٍ دُونَ حَرِّ شُعَاعِهَا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>